snippet.title: Going Under Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
Going Under is coming to Nintendo Switch, Xbox One, Playstation 4 and PC on September 24th 2020! Take on the unpaid internship from hell in this quirky roguelite! Clear failed tech-startups that have turned into dungeons! Battle their employees who have turned into monsters! Your only weapons, any junk you find lying around. Are you ready to gain 'valuable work experience'?

Wishlist Going Under on Steam: http://bit.ly/GoingUnderSteam

#GoingUnder #GoingUnderReleaseDate #IndieGames

Learn more: http://bit.ly/GoingUnderGame

About Team17 Digital Ltd
Founded in 1990, Team17 Digital Limited is a leading international games label that hosts the Worms franchise, Neon Abyss, The Escapists, Blasphemous, Overcooked, The Survivalists, Moving Out, Yooka-Laylee and many more from developers around the world. Visit www.team17.com for more info.
